org.hibernate.ogm.model.key.spi

Interface EntityKeyMetadata

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultEntityKeyMetadata

    public interface EntityKeyMetadata
    Stores metadata information common to all keys related to a given entity.
    Author:
    Emmanuel Bernard <emmanuel@hibernate.org>
